tps://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/7101/', '', 'Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Cetirizine, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Trimethobenzamide, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole', 'Ciclesonide, Mometasone furoate, Budesonide, Flunisolide, Fluticasone, Cromoglicic acid, Betamethasone, Nedocromil, Triamcinolone, Beclomethasone dipropionate, Mometasone furoate, More', 1767369485);
